180037a9710afd6b9d325c5ffadccb76a077a118.query: UPDATE orders SET cancelled = true WHERE offerer = $1::TEXT::citext AND counter < $2

64d88d952a6ed486a07ca5d33cf9613e780ec367.query:
INSERT INTO orders (
                hash,
                offerer,
                zone,
                zone_hash,
                start_time,
                end_time,
                order_type,
                total_original_consideration_items,
                counter,
                salt,
                conduit_key,
                signature
            )
                VALUES ($1, $2::TEXT::citext, $3::TEXT::citext, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, $10, $11, $12)
                ON CONFLICT (hash) DO NOTHING;

86e3e8111cb02ec2bc2ba1d0a1816ccf67802ef2.query:
INSERT INTO considerations (
                    position,
                    "order",
                    item_type,
                    token,
                    identifier_or_criteria,
                    start_amount,
                    end_amount,
                    recipient
                )
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4::TEXT::citext, $5, $6, $7, $8::TEXT::citext)
                    ON CONFLICT ("order", position) DO NOTHING;
